Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya ya karu sosai a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris na 2020.
Cutar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) tana da irin wannan yanayin a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa duk da matakai daban-daban na ci gabanta a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da Italiya ta fuskanta, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da kuma ma'aikatun kulawa mai tsanani su ƙara kasancewa a shirye don samun masu cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar magani, musamman ma kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019 an samu wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar huhu a birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
