Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da SARS-CoV-2 an fara kiranta da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bisa ga bayanan da ake da su a yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin ɗari na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, cututtukan numfashi tare da ciwon huhu ko kuma ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin mutane suna warkewa.
Kimanin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na COVID-19 suna samun ciwo mai tsanani wanda ke bukatar asibiti, kuma kashi 6 cikin ɗari na ciwo yana samun ciwo mai tsanani wanda ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su a asibiti da COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4%.
Wannan binciken ya bincika yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da kuma a Burtaniya kuma ya kwatanta shi da yanayin lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Mun kuma gwada adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da kuma Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
Bayan barkewar cutar a China, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe, kuma yanzu a sauran sassan duniya, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba daidai da yadda ta faru a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris na shekarar 2020, babban daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya sanar da annobar COVID-19.
A cikin mujallar Eurosurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Mista Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, wanda ya cika ka'idodin WHO don gano cutar.
An samu mutane uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a EU/EEA a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020  dukkansu uku sun dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris na shekarar 2020, an gano masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, tare da a cikin lokacin daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan kwanan wata an sami kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, daga cikinsu akwai 17,750, ciki har da 1,441 da suka mutu, a Italiya kadai.
Ƙayyade yawan cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan masu kamuwa da cutar
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace kasa a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe, daga tushe na hukuma, kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya na waɗannan ƙasashe, hukumomin kula da kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanin don bincika yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
A matsayin mai nuna yawan yaduwar cutar COVID-19, an ƙididdige yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 bisa ga yadda COVID-19 ke gudana a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa a karfe 8:00 na ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
Yanayin ci gaban cututtukan cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma a cikin Burtaniya gaba ɗaya sun yi daidai da yanayin da aka gani a lardin Hubei na China (Figure 1).
Cutar COVID-19 mai yawa a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya gaba ɗaya ta fara ƙaruwa a kusan ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 an sami tsalle mai girma a wannan adadin (karin bayani).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga karuwar yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun ga irin wannan karuwar cutar COVID-19 (karin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da irin wannan adadin a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bisa ga wannan, jimillar adadin waɗanda aka riga aka samu a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe a wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma a Burtaniya, ya yi daidai da adadin da aka samu a Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka samu da cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya na ƙaruwa sosai.
Yanayin da ake gani na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar ta na yaduwa a cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Kuma wannan duk da cewa akwai matakai daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, da bambancin matakan amsawa da hukumomin kiwon lafiyar ƙasa ke ɗauka, da kuma yiwuwar bambancin ƙa'idodin ganewar cutar da kuma ƙa'idodin zaɓin marasa lafiya don yin gwajin COVID-19, gami da gwajin "inversor".
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun ruwaito cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 na bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun lura cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a wadannan yankuna sun cika sosai.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya da COVID-19 asibitoci da (ko) sashen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin EU/EEA ne kawai game da kashi 6 cikin ɗari da kuma kashi 1 cikin ɗari na shari'o'i daidai da haka (ba a gabatar da bayanai ba).
Amma, ya kamata a riƙa tattara wannan bayanin a kai a kai don a ƙara yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da kuma waɗanda suka mutu.
Bisa ga sakamakon bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-2011 a Turai, akwai bambanci mai yawa a yawan gadaje a sashen jinya mai tsanani da kuma sashen kula da marasa lafiya mai tsanani: daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 gadaje ga mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa wasu ƙasashe na iya samun wadata ko ƙarancin wadata fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje a cikin ɗakunan kulawa mai tsanani da ɗakunan kulawa mai tsanani a kowace 100,000 a cikin 2010-2011).
Rahoton ECDC na shida da aka sabunta na sakamakon kimanta hadarin COVID-19 ya gabatar da yanayin yin kwaikwayon kayan aiki na tsarin kiwon lafiya tare da kimanta bayanan asibiti na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, lokacin da haɗarin rashin isassun gadaje a sashen kulawa mai tsanani ya wuce 90%.
Tun da yake a yanzu an rarraba masu kamuwa da cutar zuwa wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da kuma asibitocin jinya suna kula da yawan jama'a na wani yanki, ana ba da shawarar a ba da bayanai game da kamuwa da cutar da kuma adadin gadaje a asibitocin jinya a matakin 2 na Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar Ƙididdigar (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata kasashe, asibitoci da kuma ma'aikatun kulawa mai zurfi su kasance a shirye don yanayin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 na dogon lokaci, da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita da kuma musamman kulawa mai zurfi, kamar yadda ake gani a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda rahoton ECDC na kwanan nan ya nuna, gaggawa, tsinkaya da kuma tsarin da aka tsara don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2 yana da mahimmanci, tare da sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa rage sakamako, saboda, bisa ga ƙididdigar ƙaruwar ƙaruwar cututtuka, masu yanke shawara da asibitoci na iya samun isasshen lokaci don yin tunani, ɗauka da daidaita amsoshin su idan ba a ɗauki irin waɗannan matakan ba.
Rahoton na gaggawa na tantance hadarin ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a da ake so a rage tasirin cutar.
Kasashe suna da ɗan lokaci kaɗan da za su iya ƙara ƙoƙarin sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage nauyin tsarin kiwon lafiyarsu.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa, tsarin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashe na EU/EEA zai fuskanci yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Cutar cutar korona ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta samo asali daga cutar korona mai saurin numfashi (SARS) ta nau'i na 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta zama bala'i ga bil'adama: a halin yanzu fiye da mutane 3,000 ne suka mutu a China da sauran kasashen duniya, kuma adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ya zarce 80,000.
Kamar SARS-CoV da ya haifar da ciwon numfashi mai tsanani a dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya samun cutar daga batsa kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar amfani da irin wannan hanyar.
Ko da yake COVID-19 ba shi da tsanani sosai kuma ba ya kashe mutane sosai kamar SARS, amma yana da saurin yaɗuwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, maza fiye da mata.
A cikin amsa ga karuwar littattafai game da sabon cutar, wannan talifin ya ba da cikakken bayani game da batun bincike mai saurin bunƙasa.
Za mu bincika fannoni na asali na kamuwa da cuta, ilmin cuta, ilmin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da kuma rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna fatan cewa wannan bincike zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai haɗari.
Bikin bazara (Sinanci Sabuwar Shekara) wanda ya faɗi a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa gani ba ga duk Sinawa, waɗanda saboda barkewar sabon kamuwa da kwayar cutar, an bukaci su zauna a gida a duk lokacin bikin da makonni da yawa bayan haka.
Bisa la'akari da irin kamannin da ke tsakanin cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da barkewar cutar SARS a shekarar 2003, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020 ta sanya wa wannan cutar suna SARS-CoV-2, kuma cutar da ke tattare da shi  cutar coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta yadu cikin sauri a duk fadin kasar, daga nan kuma zuwa kusan kasashe 50 na duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, an gano sama da mutane 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 sun warke, sama da marasa lafiya 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin farko na al'umma" kuma yana iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an sami wallafe-wallafe sama da 200 game da COVID-19, gami da labarai game da kwayar cutar, cutar, ilimin halitta, ganewar asali da magani, tun daga rahoton farko na Janairu 7, 2020, wanda ya gano jerin kwayar cutar da aka ware daga wasu marasa lafiya.
Wannan bita na ƙoƙari ne na taƙaita sakamakon bincike a cikin sabon da kuma saurin bunkasa fannin.
A duk inda za mu iya, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wasu cututtukan coronavirus  Coronavirus na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS), wanda ya barke a shekarar 2012.
Za mu kuma tattauna abubuwan da aka sani a yanzu game da rigakafi da kuma yadda ake tsinkayar cutar, da kuma wasu batutuwa masu muhimmanci.
Kwayar cutar korona ta kasance a cikin masu cutar da ba ta da haɗari ga mutum kuma galibi tana haifar da kusan kashi 15 cikin ɗari na cututtukan numfashi na kowacce shekara 4.
Duk da haka, mun sha fama da cututtukan korona masu saurin yaduwa a cikin wannan karni sau biyu, wato SARS-CoV-2 da kuma MERS-CoV, wadanda suka fara bullowa a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012 kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da ke da yawan cutar da kuma mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine fashewar cutar coronavirus ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1, rahoton farko game da tarin cututtukan cutar huhu da ba a san asalin su ba ya shiga Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta kasa ta kasar Sin daga birnin Wuhan a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019.
Bayan kwana bakwai, sai aka fitar da tsarin kwayoyin cutar.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an samu mace-mace ta farko a birnin Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
