A wasu layin kwayar cutar korona kuma an yi amfani da wasu layin da ke da takamaiman bayani.
Bisa bambance-bambance a jerin sunayen sunadarai, an raba kwayar cutar corona zuwa nau'i hudu (alpha-, beta-, gamma- da delta-coronavirus), yayin da nau'in beta-coronavirus ya hada da yawancin kwayar cutar ta mutum kuma an raba shi zuwa layi hudu (A, B, C da D).
Akwai shaidar ilimin halittar halittu da ke nuna cewa mafi yawan alpha da beta coronavirus sun fito ne daga bat da kuma masu ciwon daji, yayin da tsuntsaye  su ne babban wurin ajiye gama da delta coronaviruses.
A cikin dubun dubatan shekaru, ƙwayoyin cuta na corona sun ci gaba da ƙetare iyakokin tsakanin jinsuna, kuma wasu daga cikinsu sun samo asali zuwa cututtukan cututtukan da ke da haɗari ga mutane.
A yau an san mutane bakwai da suka kamu da cutar korona.
Waɗannan sun haɗa da kwayar cutar HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 na ɗan adam.
Sauran beta-coronavirus guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), coronavirus mai saurin numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da kuma SARS-CoV-2 mai saurin numfashi mai tsanani na nau'i na biyu.
Kwayar cutar korona ta mutum HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi da (ko) zawo.
Akasin haka, ƙwayoyin cuta na SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da kuma SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano kwanan nan suna da cututtuka sosai, suna haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin ƙididdigar yawan marasa lafiya tare da yiwuwar ci gaba da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (ARS) da bayyanar cututtuka na waje da huhu.
An samo zaren farko na kwayar cutar HCoV-229E, B814, daga samfurin da aka cire daga hanci da hanci na marasa lafiya masu sanyi a cikin shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, bincike mai zurfi ya kawo ƙarin bayani game da ƙwayoyin cuta HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 waɗanda ke haifar da alamun kamuwa da cuta a cikin gida.
Hakika, kafin barkewar cutar SARS, an yi imani cewa kamuwa da cutar korona ba ta da lahani.
Barkewar cutar SARS a 2003 na ɗaya daga cikin munanan annobar cutar a tarihin yanzu; sama da mutane 8,000 suka kamu da cutar, kuma yawan mutuwar kusan kashi 10 ne.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar MERS ta haifar da annoba mai tsawo a yankin Larabawa, kuma ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe na duniya.
Sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum (2019-nCoV) da aka gano a shekarar 2019, wanda daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, shine wanda ke haifar da annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020 ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120, kuma adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar ya wuce mutane 91,000.
An ba da sanarwar gaggawa, kuma duniya ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar korona guda bakwai na mutum sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi, ko dai daga batsa, ko kuma daga beraye ko kuma daga dabbobi.
Bayanai da yawa sun nuna cewa kwayar cutar korona ta mutum ta samo asali ne daga batsa, wadda kwayoyin cutar suka dace da ita kuma ba su da cutar, amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta jefa kalubale ga kasar Sin da kuma duniya baki daya ta fuskar kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da kuma ɗabi'a.
Binciken tsarin kwayar cutar korona ta mutum zai taimaka wajen fahimtar tarihin halitta, abubuwan da ke motsa juyin halitta da kuma abubuwan da ke hana yaduwar cutar tsakanin jinsuna.
Zai iya kuma ba da shawara ko kuma hanzarta gano maɓuɓɓugar SARS-CoV-2 da ke tsakanin da kuma mai yaduwa, wanda ke da muhimmanci wajen hana sake yaduwar cutar a nan gaba.
Wannan bita ya ƙunshi bayanai na gaba ɗaya game da asalin dabbobi, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma cutar coronavirus na ɗan adam.
Musamman, mun gano kuma mun bincika wannan fasalin na kowa: ƙwayoyin cuta na asali waɗanda suka haifar da kwayar cutar coronavirus na ɗan adam ba su da cutar ga masu ɗaukar su, amma suna da cutar bayan watsawa tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon mai ɗaukar hoto.
Muna kuma nazarin yanayin juyin halittar kwayar cutar korona ta mutum, wanda ke nuna cewa yawanci yawan kamuwa da cuta yana tare da raguwar cutar.
A cikin wannan mahallin ana kuma duba sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ke faruwa a yanzu.
An san cutar korona ta dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin a fara gano kwayar cutar B814 na kwayar cutar HCoV-229E daga samfurin da aka cire daga hanci da hanci na marasa lafiya masu sanyi, an sami nau'ikan kwayar cutar korona a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da suka kamu da cutar, ciki har da turke, mice, shanu, aladu, kuliyoyi da karnuka.
An gano kwayar cutar korona guda bakwai a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
A cikin tebur 1 an nuna taƙaitaccen tarihin gano kwayar cutar korona ta mutum cikin tsari na lokaci.
An samo kwayar cutar HCoV-229E ta farko daga samfurin da aka ɗauka daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya tare da lalacewar kamuwa da cutar ta sama a cikin 1966; daga baya wannan kwayar cutar ta daidaita don haɓaka a cikin layukan ƙwayoyin huhu na WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da kwayar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi, ciki har da ciwon kai, hancin, rashin jin daɗi da ciwon makogwaro, yayin da zazzabi da tari suka bayyana a kashi 1020 cikin dari.
Daga baya, a shekara ta 1967, an gano kwayar cutar HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun jiki kuma an yi amfani da ita a cikin kwakwalwar linzamin kwamfuta.
Alamomin asibiti na kamuwa da kwayar cutar HCoV-OC43 suna kama da bayyanar kamuwa da kwayar cutar HCoV-229E, alamun da ba su bambanta da lalacewa ta wasu cututtukan cututtukan numfashi, kamar su ƙwayoyin cuta na mura na nau'in A da rhinoviruses.
Dukansu kwayar HCoV-229E da kwayar HCoV-OC43 suna da yaduwa a ko'ina a duniya kuma yawanci ana watsa su a lokacin hunturu a matsakaitan wurare.
Yawancin lokaci, lokacin da wannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu suke kwance ba ya kai mako guda, sai kuma bayan haka sai a yi rashin lafiya na kusan makonni biyu.
Binciken da aka yi a kan masu sa kai ya nuna cewa mutanen da ke da lafiya da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoV-229E suna da sanyi mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya da suke da ƙarancin garkuwar jiki ne kawai suke da ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Cutar SARS, wanda kuma aka sani da  annobar cutar huhu ta atypical, ita ce ta farko a tarihin ɗan adam da aka rubuta ta da kyau ta hanyar cutar coronavirus ta ɗan adam, kuma cutar ta haifar da cutar SARS-CoV, ta uku daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na ɗan adam da aka gano.
An gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
A lokacin annobar SARS an samu mutum 8,096 da suka kamu da cutar kuma mutum 774 suka mutu, kuma cutar ta bazu zuwa kasashe da nahiyoyi da dama.
Ba tare da la'akari da masu yaduwa ba, an kiyasta cewa kowane mutum da ya kamu da cutar zai iya kamuwa da wasu mutane biyu; lokacin incubation ya kasance daga kwanaki 4 zuwa 7, kuma mafi girman nauyin kwayar cutar ya kasance a ranar 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV sun fara da ciwon tsoka, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin jin daɗi da kuma sanyi, kuma daga baya sun sami rashin numfashi, tari da kuma rashin numfashi.
Abubuwan da suka fi faruwa a cikin SARS su ne lymphopenia, rashin daidaito a gwajin hanta da kuma yawan creatine kinase.
A cikin marasa lafiya da ke da cutar SARS, an kuma ga lalacewar alveolar diffuse, ƙaruwar ƙwayoyin epithelial da kuma ƙaruwar macrophage.
Kusan kashi 2030 na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma yin amfani da iska mai guba.
A irin wannan mawuyacin hali, ban da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, wasu gabobin jiki na iya kamuwa da cutar, ciki har da gabobin ciki, hanta da koda, wanda yawanci yakan haifar da guguwar cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa, musamman ga marasa lafiya da ke da rauni.
An fara gano kwayar cutar ne daga kwayar cutar da aka yi a bude a cikin huhu na wani dangin wanda ya zo Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga lokacin an yi gagarumar kokarin bincike kan kwayar cutar korona ta mutum.
A ƙarshen 2004, an gano HCoV-NL63 a cikin jariri mai wata bakwai a Netherlands.
Da farko an gano cewa ya fi shafar yara ƙanana, tsofaffi, da marasa lafiya da ke da rashin garkuwar jiki da kuma cututtukan numfashi.
Cutar da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa ta ƙunshi bayyanar cututtuka kamar su kumburi, cutar hawan jiki, zazzabi da kuma cutar sankarar bargo.
Wani bincike na 'yanci ya nuna cewa an gano wannan kwayar cutar ne daga hanci da aka samo daga wani yaro ɗan wata takwas da ke Netherlands da ke fama da ciwon huhu.
An gano wannan cuta ne a Netherlands, amma a gaskiya ta yaɗu ko'ina.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 na haifar da kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi da suka fi yawa, kuma yawan cututtukan da ke haifar da shi yana zuwa a farkon bazara, bazara da kuma hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar laringitis ta ƙuntatawa, wanda kuma ake kira croup.
An gano HCoV-HKU1 a Hong Kong a wannan shekarar daga wani mutum mai shekara 71 da aka kwantar da shi a asibiti da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon kumburin huhu.
Baya ga ciwon huhu da kuma cutar sankarar bargo, ana danganta HCoV-HKU1 da cutar asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, an gano kwayar cutar HCoV-HKU1, wadda ke haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi na numfashi a duk duniya.
Duk waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda huɗu na mutum waɗanda ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti sun dace da mutane sosai, kuma sauyin da ke haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da cuta ba shi da tabbas, kodayake akwai abubuwan da suka faru kuma ba a san dalilin su ba, kamar yadda yake a cikin wani misali mai wuya tare da ƙaramin nau'in HCoV-NL63 wanda aka ba da rahoton kwanan nan cewa ya haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a cikin ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a China.
A al'ada, ta hanyar samun damar watsawa da kuma adanawa cikin jikin mutum, wadannan kwayar cutar korona ta mutum ba ta da kwayar cuta ko kuma cutar.
An fara gano cutar coronavirus na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) a shekarar 2012 a Saudi Arabiya daga huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da ke fama da ciwon huhu mai tsanani da kuma rashin aikin koda.
Yawancin lab da aka tabbatar da su sun faru ne a Gabas ta Tsakiya, amma an samu wasu cututtuka a kasashen Turai da Tunisia da suka kai ga yaduwar cutar ta hanyar kamuwa da ita ta hanyar kusanci.
Wani kuma annobar ta biyu da ta tabbatar da mutane 186 ta faru ne a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015.
Alamar asibiti na ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) yana kama da alamun cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS)  duka cututtuka biyu suna da ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, mutane da yawa da ke fama da cutar MERS sun kuma samu rashin aikin koda, wanda har yanzu ya bambanta MERS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da kwayar cutar korona da ke yaduwa zuwa ga mutane.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin dari na marasa lafiya suna da alamun ciwon ciki, kamar zawo da kuma amai.
Ya zuwa ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an sami fiye da mutane 2,500 da aka tabbatar da su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje na ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya tare da yawan mutuwar (34.4%), saboda haka ana daukar MERS-CoV daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi kashe mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba na 2019, an gano tarin marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar huhu a birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin, wanda yanzu idan aka duba baya, ana danganta shi da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai tsanani nau'i na 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da cewa barkewar cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar numfashi ta duniya ta zama gaggawa a fannin kiwon lafiyar jama'a, kuma cutar kanta ta sami sunan coronavirus infection 19 (COVID-19).
A ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020, an samu mutane 90 053 da suka kamu da cutar a duniya, inda yawan mutuwar mutane ya kai kusan kashi 3.4 cikin dari.
Ya kamata a lura cewa yawan mutuwar mutane a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin ya kai kashi 4.2 bisa dari, kuma a kasashen waje ya kai kashi 1.2 bisa dari.
SARS-CoV-2, kamar SARS da MERS, yana haifar da mummunar kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi, wanda ke nuna zazzabi, tari da kuma rashin numfashi.
Wasu marasa lafiya ma suna da zawo.
Ciwon huhu yana ɗaya daga cikin alamun da ke da tsanani kuma yana iya saurin zama ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Duk da kamanceceniya tsakanin SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2, saboda yawan daidaiton jerin nucleotides (82%), waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta, duk da haka, suna samar da rassan bishiyar phylogenetic daban-daban.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da cutar amma yana da damar watsawa fiye da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu wasu cututtuka na SARS-CoV-2 da ba su da alamun cutar, wanda ke nuna cewa cutar tana iya yaduwa cikin sauri a duniya.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran kwayar cutar korona guda shida na mutum ya nuna muhimman kamance da bambance-bambance.
Na farko, kwayar cutar korona da ke yaduwa ga mutane tana da irin wannan lokacin da take kwance da kuma tsawon lokacin da take kwance.
A wannan yanayin, SARS-CoV-2 yana nuna irin wannan yanayin kamar sauran kwayar cutar korona guda shida na ɗan adam.
Na biyu, a cikin yanayin bayyanar cututtuka, COVID-19 yana tsakanin SARS-CoV da kuma kwayar cutar coronavirus guda huɗu na mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar daga asibiti (watau HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, bayyanar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta yi kama da wanda ake samu a cikin kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum, wadda ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti, ciki har da bayyanar da ba ta da takamaiman yanayi, bayyanar cututtuka masu sauƙi ko ma rashin bayyanar cututtuka.
A gefe guda, kamar yadda yake a SARS-CoV, za a iya gano ƙaramin rukunin manyan shari'o'in COVID-19, ko da yake rabo a nan ya ɗan ƙasa.
Na uku, ana kuma lura da wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa a cikin hanyar watsa SARS-CoV-2 da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar korona ta mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar a waje da asibiti, da kuma SARS-CoV.
A gefe guda, SARS-CoV-2 yana da yaduwar cutar kamar yadda kwayar cutar korona ta mutum take da yaduwar cutar a waje da asibiti.
A gefe guda, har yanzu ana bukatar a bincika ko SARS-CoV-2 yana raguwa da kowane sauyin kwayar cutar (watau kamuwa da kowane mutum na gaba), kamar yadda yake a SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti, ana iya gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta.
Har yanzu ba mu amsa tambayar ko hanyar watsa SARS-CoV-2 ta bakin jini tana da muhimmanci (aƙalla a wasu yanayi) kamar yadda take a SARS-CoV.
Tambayar yiwuwar yanayi na SARS-CoV-2 da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar korona ta mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti, na da ban sha'awa.
Koyaya, ci gaban gaba na barkewar COVID-19 zai dogara ne akan fasalin SARS-CoV-2, gami da yaduwa, cutar, da kuma ci gaba da yaduwa bayan ya wuce ta hanyar mutane.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar korona guda huɗu da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti da kuma bayyanar cututtuka masu sauƙi sun daidaita da mutane sosai.
A wani bangare kuma, wataƙila mutane ne suka daidaita da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda huɗu na ɗan adam.
A wasu kalmomi, dukansu za a iya cewa su ne kawai suka tsira daga annobar korona a baya.
Kwayar cutar korona ta mutum da ke haifar da mummunar cuta a cikin mutane, da kuma mutanen da kwayar cutar korona ta mutum ke haifar da mummunar cuta, ba su tsira ba.
Don hakan ya faru, dole ne kwayar cutar korona ta ɗan adam ta ninka a jikin ɗan adam yadda ya kamata don samun tarin ƙwayoyin halittar da ke adawa da abubuwan da ke hana mai ɗaukar hoto.
A wannan ma'anar, yayin da annobar SARS-CoV-2 ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa kuma mutane da yawa suna kamuwa da ita, za a sami damar cewa cutar za ta iya daidaita kanta ga mutane.
Idan ya dace, zai yi wuya a hana shi ya yaɗu tsakanin mutane ta hanyar keɓewa ko kuma wasu hanyoyin sarrafa cututtuka.
An yi shekaru ana yaduwar wasu nau'o'in cutar korona guda hudu a cikin jama'a, wadanda ke haifar da sanyi a cikin mutanen da suke da garkuwar jiki.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba sa bukatar dabba mai riƙe da ruwa.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV ba su daidaita da mutane yadda ya kamata ba, kuma ba za a iya ci gaba da watsa su tsakanin mutane ba.
Suna bukatar su ci gaba da haifuwa a cikin tasoshin dabbobin da kuma neman damar shiga cikin mutane masu karɓa, watakila ta hanyar daya ko fiye na matsakaici ko masu haɓaka.
SARS-CoV-2 yana da halaye masu kama da SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV, da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta huɗu na HCoV.
Yana da sauƙin yaduwa kamar HCoVs na waje, aƙalla a yanzu.
Amma ya fi cutar HCoVs da ake samu a waje da asibiti, kuma ba shi da cutar SARS-CoV ko MERS-CoV.
Abin da ya rage shi ne ganin ko ya dace da 'yan Adam kuma ko zai iya zama a cikin yanayin 'yan Adam ba tare da tanki ba ko kuma tare da dabba mai ɗaukar hoto.
Kafin mu tattauna asalin dabbobi na kwayar cutar HCoVs, zai taimaka mana mu tattauna ma'anar da kuma halayen masu ɗaukar kwayar cutar HCoVs na juyin halitta, na halitta, na tsaka-tsaki, mai haɓaka, da na tanadi.
Dabba na iya zama mai ɗaukar kwayar cutar HCoV idan ta ɗauki wani magaji mai dangantaka da juna wanda yake da irin wannan daidaito a matakin jerin nucleotides.
Kwayar cutar ta asali tana da sauyi sosai kuma ba ta haifar da cuta a cikin wannan mai ɗaukar hoto.
Hakazalika, mai ɗaukar kwayar cutar HCoV yana ɗaukar kwayar cutar a kai a kai na dogon lokaci.
A duka biyun, masu dauke da cutar sun kamu da cutar ta halitta kuma su ne masu dauke da HCoV ko kuma kwayar cutar da ta haife su.
Akasin haka, idan HCoV ya shiga cikin mai ɗaukar hoto na tsakanin nan da nan kafin ko kusa da lokacin da aka kai shi ga ɗan adam, ba a daidaita shi da kyau ga sabon mai ɗaukar hoto ba kuma sau da yawa yana haifar da cuta.
Wannan mai watsawa na iya zama tushen cutar ta ɗan adam kuma ya zama mai ɗaukar hoto, yana ba da damar kwayar cutar ta ninka da sauri, sannan ta watsa shi ga mutane, yana ƙara yawan kamuwa da mutane.
HCoV zai iya ɗaukar kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar toshe idan ba zai iya jure watsawa a cikin mai ɗaukar hoto ba.
Akasin haka, ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs na iya daidaitawa ga mai ɗaukar hoto na tsakiya har ma da kafa ƙarancin ƙarancin lokaci.
A wannan yanayin, mai ɗaukar na'urar tsakiya ya zama mai ɗaukar tanki na halitta.
Bayanan cututtuka sun nuna cewa ba a taɓa samun cutar SARS ba, kuma an gano cewa an yi ta da dabbobi masu farauta.
Ƙarin bincike na yawan ƙwayar cutar ya nuna cewa yawan kwayoyin cutar IgG zuwa cutar SARS-CoV a cikin masu sayar da dabbobi ya fi na sauran mutane.
Ciftawar Himalayanci (Paguma larvata) da kare mai kama da naman-dumi a kasuwannin dabbobi masu rai sun zama farkon waɗanda aka gano cewa suna dauke da ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da SARS-CoV.
An tabbatar da hakan ta hanyar cewa bayan an kawar da duk wani ciwon daji a kasuwanni, ba a sake samun rahoton cutar SARS ba.
A lokaci guda, an bayar da rahoton cewa a cikin ciyawa na Himalayan da ke rayuwa a cikin yanayi ko a gonaki kuma ba a samu a kasuwa ba, ba a gano SARS-CoV a mafi yawan lokuta, wanda ya ba da damar yanke shawarar cewa ciyawa na Himalayan na iya zama kawai a matsayin mai ɗaukar hoto na tsaka-tsaki, ba kamar tanadin SARS-CoV na halitta ba.
Abin lura ne cewa, saboda kashi 80% na dabbobi daban-daban a kasuwannin Guangzhou suna da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, ba za a iya ware yiwuwar cewa yawancin nau'in ƙananan dabbobi masu shayarwa na iya zama masu ɗaukar kwayar cutar ba.
