A wannan ranar ne aka kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (mutane 176 daga jirgin farko da 39  daga na biyu, da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi haya) daga Wuhan, aka kai su sansanin sojin Kanada na Trenton kuma aka sanya su a cikin keɓewa na tsawon makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama da ke dauke da 'yan kasar Canada 185 da aka kwashe daga birnin Wuhan ya sauka a sansanin jiragen sama na CFB Trenton.
A ranar 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu, hukumomin Australia sun kwashe 'yan kasar su 277 suka sanya su a wani wurin zama na wucin gadi a tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka mayar da shi cibiyar killacewa, inda suka zauna na tsawon kwanaki 14.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, jirgin saukar jiragen sama na New Zealand ya isa Auckland; fasinjojinsa (ciki har da wasu daga Ostiraliya da yankin Asiya da Pacific) an sanya su a cikin keɓewa a sansanin sojan ruwa na Vangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe 'yan kasar da ke cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, jirgin sama mai dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, jirgin saman kamfanin jiragen sama na South African Airways, wanda gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya, ya tashi tare da 'yan Afirka ta Kudu 112 a cikin jirgin.
An yi wa fasinjoji gwajin lafiya kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da suka nuna alamun cutar coronavirus a China don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka nuna cewa ba su da cutar coronavirus ne kawai aka kwashe.
An yi gwajin dukkan 'yan kasar Afirka ta Kudu, ciki har da ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji, kuma a matsayin kariya, an sanya su a cikin keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta sanar da cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun tura taimakon su zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin da ke karatu a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don tarawa da kuma tura kayan agaji zuwa yankunan kasar Sin da cutar ta shafa, tare da wani rukuni daga Chicago da aka ruwaito cewa sun aika da na'urori masu numfashi 50,000 na N95 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa samar da maganin rigakafi da maganin cutar coronavirus, da kuma kare mutanen da ke fuskantar hadarin cutar a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya daga barazanar cutar.
Interaksyon ta ruwaito cewa a ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairu, gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska na likita 200,000 ga Philippines bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa birnin Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura dala miliyan 2.26 zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta kuma ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska na likita miliyan daya zuwa Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika kayan aikin likita zuwa can, Rasha  sama da tan 13 na magunguna, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safofin hannu na likita miliyan 18, Jamus ta aika da kayan aikin likita daban-daban ciki har da kayan kariya 10,000, Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na magunguna, sannan ta yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafin kuɗi ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Bayan da yanayin ya daidaita a China, kasar ta kuma aika da taimako ga sauran ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, Sin, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da magunguna da masana zuwa Italiya don taimakawa al'ummar kasar wajen shawo kan barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jack Ma ya aika wa kungiyar tarayyar Afirka, Addis Ababa, Habasha, da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan shida da kuma rigunan kariya dubu 60 domin kungiyar ta rarraba su a cikin kasashe mambobinta.
Daga baya kuma ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin IVL guda biyar zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar magunguna ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a kasar Sin.
Misali, Spain ta janye kayan gwajin cutar korona na kasar Sin 58,000 da ke da kashi 30 cikin 100 na daidaito, yayin da Netherlands ta janye kayan rufe fuska na kasar Sin 600,000 da suka lalace.
Belgium ta kuma janye abin rufe fuska na kiwon lafiya 100,000 da ba su dace da amfani ba: an yi zaton cewa an yi su ne a China, amma daga baya aka gano cewa sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A wani bangaren kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon kasar Sin a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya fara gudanar da ayyukan agaji na gaggawa ga kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya WHO ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen yaki da annobar da kuma dakile yaduwar cutar.
WHO ta lura da bambance-bambance tsakanin yanayin annobar cutar huhu ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da ɓoye bayanai, wanda ke hana cutar da kuma hana yaduwar ta, da kuma rikicin yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ke ba da sabunta bayanai akai-akai don kauce wa fargaba a ranar Sabuwar Shekarar kasar Sin.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar da gwamnatin tsakiya ta yanke na hana zirga-zirgar ababen hawa a birnin Wuhan, kakakin WHO Gauden Galea ya ce, ko da yake wannan matakin ba shawarar WHO ba ne, amma kuma  muhimmin tabbaci ne na cika alkawuran da aka dauka na dakile annobar a inda ta fi yaduwa, kuma ya kira ta marar da aka taba gani a tarihin kiwon lafiyar jama'a.  A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, bayan tabbatar da iyawar kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen kasar Sin da kuma karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar a wasu kasashe, WHO ta ayyana gaggawa a tsarin kiwon lafiyar jama'a mai muhimmanci a duniya (PICHE); wannan shine karo na shida tun daga shekarar 2009 da aka fara amfani da irin wannan matakin a lokacin annobar cutar.
Darakta Janar na WHO, Mr. Tedros Adhanom ya ce sanarwar PHEIC na da hadarin yaduwa a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Da yake tsokaci kan takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Mista Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili na matakan da ke hana zirga-zirgar kasa da kasa da kasuwanci" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar a takaita kasuwanci da zirga-zirga ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi al'ummar duniya su ba da dala miliyan 675 domin samar da shirye-shiryen farfadowa a kasashe masu karancin kudin shiga, inda ta yi kira ga kasashen da basu da tsarin gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, duk da cewa cutar ba ta kai kasashen ba.
Mista Tedros ya kuma bayyana cewa "ma'aunin shirye-shiryenmu" shine yadda muke shirye don cutar ta mafi rauni", kuma ya yi kira ga al'ummar duniya "suyi zabi: su saka hannun jari a yau ko su biya nan gaba". A taron manema labarai da aka gudanar a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanya sunan cutar a hukumance  COVID-19.
A wannan ranar Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, António Guterres ya amince ya ba da "ikon iya aiki na dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya" a matsayin amsar matsalar.
Sakamakon haka, an kafa rukunin kula da rikice-rikicen Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don daidaita duk matakan da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ɗauka; WHO ta ce waɗannan matakan za su "mai da hankali kan maganin kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya amfani da ƙwarewarsu don magance barkewar cutar a cikin mafi girman zamantakewa da tattalin arziki. "
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, WHO da China sun fara kafa wata kungiya ta musamman ta hadin gwiwa wacce ta samar da kwararru na kasa da kasa da ma'aikatan WHO a cikin kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen daidaita yanayin cikin gida da kuma kimanta tsananin cutar da yaduwar ta, ta shirya tarurruka da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin kasa, da kuma tafiye-tafiye zuwa wuraren don kimanta inganta matakan amsawa a matakin lardi da gundumomi, gami da birane da yankunan karkara. A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ce duniya tana bukatar yin karin shiri don yiwuwar cutar ta coronavirus, tana mai lura cewa lokaci bai yi ba tukuna da za a kira cutar a matsayin annoba, amma duk da haka, ya kamata kasashe su kasance a shirye.
Lokacin da annobar ta bulla a Iran, WHO ta tura wata ƙungiya mai haɗin gwiwa don kimanta yanayin. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a ƙara yawan yiwuwar yaduwar cutar ta coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mai matukar girma" a matsayin mafi girman matakin shiri da haɗari.
Mike Ryan, babban daraktan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin a cikin wata sanarwa: "Wannan gwaji ne ga kowace gwamnati a duniya kan shirye-shiryen da take da shi don ganin abin da ke faruwa: lokaci ya yi da za a yi aiki.
Ya kuma jaddada cewa, amsa mai kyau zai iya taimakawa duniya wajen kauce wa mafi munin yanayin da zai iya faruwa.
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanan na yanzu ba su da wani dalili da zai sa jami'an kiwon lafiya su ayyana annobar a duniya, ya kuma kara da cewa, sanar da annobar zai nuna cewa "a zahiri mun yarda da gaskiyar cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kasance cikin hadarin kamuwa da wannan kwayar cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris ne WHO ta ayyana annobar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar na WHO ya bayyana cewa WHO  tana da matukar damuwa game da yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar, da kuma rashin yin komai game da matsalar. WHO tana fuskantar mummunan suka saboda yadda ake ganin rashin dacewar batun cutar, gami da sanar da gaggawa na kiwon lafiyar jama'a da kuma rarraba cutar a matsayin annoba.
A matsayin martani ga halin da ake ciki, an gabatar da takarda neman murabus ga Darakta Janar na WHO, Mr. Tedros Adanom, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, masana na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kan hakkin dan adam sun jaddada muhimmancin kiyaye hakkin kowane mutum a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin daukar matakan ceton rai, kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin gudanar da irin wannan matakin.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko rashin inshorar lafiya ba zai zama hujja ba don nuna bambanci ga kowane rukuni na mutane.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowa yana da hakkin samun kulawar lafiya, gami da nakasassu, 'yan tsirarun al'umma, tsofaffi, wadanda suka rasa gidajensu, marasa gida, 'yan kasa da ke cikin mawuyacin yanayi, fursunoni, da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyi da ba a bayyana su ba da suke bukatar tallafin gwamnati.
Ƙungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya suna duba tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewa na rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kirkiro wani dandamali da aka tsara don samar da cikakken bayani kan matakan siyasa a kasashen duniya, da kuma samun ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Cibiyar ta na ba da bayanai game da manufofin da kasashe daban-daban (Country Policy Tracker) ke bi wajen karfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya, kawar da tasirin keɓewa da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, don taimakawa ƙasashe su koyi darussa daga juna da kuma inganta daidaitaccen martani na duniya kan cutar korona.
Gwamnatin China ta fuskanci suka daga Amurka, Ministan Ministan Burtaniya Michael Gow da Eduardo Bolsonaro, dan shugaban Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, saboda ayyukan da suka yi na magance annobar da ta fara daga lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori wasu shugabannin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CCP) a matakin lardi saboda takunkumin da suka dauka a tsakiyar kasar Sin, kuma wannan sallamar ta nuna rashin jin dadin yadda hukumomin siyasa ke mayar da martani ga barkewar cutar a wadannan yankuna.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan matakin ne don kare babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a game da barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian, sun nuna rashin amincewa da da'awar da aka yi a baya cewa barkewar cutar coronavirus ta fara ne a Wuhan, amma sun goyi bayan ka'idar makirci cewa COVID-19 ta samo asali ne a Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ta kira coronavirus  cutar Sin ko  cutar Wuhan, inda ta ce  tacewar da ake yi a China na kara tsananta yanayin cutar da ta zama annoba ta duniya, kuma wannan furucin ya sha suka daga wasu masu sharhi, wadanda suka ce wannan tsarin na nuna wariyar launin fata ne kuma  yana jan hankali daga rashin iyawar gwamnatin shugaban Amurka wajen dakile yaduwar cutar .
The Daily Beast ta samu damar samun sakon gwamnatin Amurka wanda ke dauke da wata dabarar sadarwa da ake ganin ta fito ne daga kwamitin tsaron kasa, inda aka ambaci dabarar: Dukkanin China.
An nemi mu yada wannan bayanin ta kowace hanya da za mu iya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma yin jawabai a talabijin. Kungiyoyi kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun ce kokarin da China ke yi na taimakawa kasashen da cutar ta addabi wani bangare ne na "ta'addanci" da ke neman samun tasiri a duniya.
Shugaban hukumar kula da harkokin wajen EU, Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai wani bangare na "yanayin siyasa da ya hada da fafutukar samun rinjaye ta hanyar talla da kuma abin da ake kira siyasar karimci".
Borrell ya kuma ce, "China tana ta yin taƙama wajen gabatar da ra'ayin cewa ita ce mai alhakin da kuma amintaccen abokin tarayya, ba kamar Amurka ba".
China ta kuma bukaci Amurka da ta soke takunkumin da ta kafa kan Syria da Venezuela da kuma Iran, tare da aika da tallafi ga kasashen biyu na karshe, kamar yadda aka ruwaito.
An hana Jack Ma bayar da kayan rufe fuska 100,000 ga Cuba saboda takunkumin Amurka da aka kafa a ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu.
