Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta nakalto wani babban jami'in siyasa mai suna Anonymous, wanda ya ce kashi 80 cikin 100 na taimakon Rasha ba shi da amfani ko kuma bai taimaka wa Italiya sosai ba.
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da cewa tana neman ta yi wa duniya kyau a fannin siyasa da diflomasiyya.
