Wanke hannu kafin shan magani ko yin aikin likita zai iya hana ko rage yaduwar cutar.
Babban manufar wanke hannu a fannin kiwon lafiya shi ne tsabtace hannu daga kwayoyin cuta (kwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin cuta ko wasu ƙwayoyin cuta da ke iya haifar da cuta), da kuma daga sinadarai da ke iya zama masu cutarwa ko kuma su haifar da wasu cututtuka.
Wannan hanya tana da muhimmanci musamman ga mutanen da suke dafa abinci ko kuma waɗanda suke aikin kiwon lafiya, amma yana da muhimmanci ga dukan mutane.
Wanke hannu yana da amfani sosai ga lafiyar mutum, kamar rage yaduwar mura, coronavirus da sauran cututtuka, hana kamuwa da cututtukan ciki, rage yaduwar cututtukan numfashi.
