Dole ne a samu "mahimman shiga" na duk "masu ruwa da tsaki" ciki har da masana kiwon lafiyar jama'a da wakilan kungiyoyin da aka yi wa kauracewa. The German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) da Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) sun kuma wallafa jerin sharuddan su.
Google da Apple sun gabatar da shirin su na hadin gwiwa don magance matsalar sa ido na dindindin, wanda shine cire tsarin bin diddigin daga tsarin aiki na na'urorin su da zarar babu bukatar hakan.
A wasu ƙasashe, ana amfani da hanyar sa ido ta hanyar sadarwa maimakon aikace-aikace, wanda ke kawar da buƙatar saukar da aikace-aikacen da kuma yiwuwar guje wa sa ido.
An amince da yin amfani da hanyar sa ido a Isra'ila.
Hanyoyin sadarwa da ke da damar samun bayanan wurin da aka samo su ma suna da babbar matsalar tsare sirri.
Koyaya, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabobin tsakiya ya kamata su sami damar zuwa bayanan sirri game da wurin ba; an tsara wasu tsarin tsare sirri waɗanda ke amfani da sabobin tsakiya kawai don sadarwa (duba sashe a ƙasa).
A Koriya ta Kudu, an yi amfani da tsarin bin diddigin lambobin sadarwa wanda ba ya amfani da aikace-aikace a matsayin tushen.
Maimakon amfani da aikace-aikacen musamman, tsarin ya tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban-daban, gami da bayanan sa ido na na'urorin hannu da ma'amaloli na katin, sannan ya haɗa su don ƙirƙirar sanarwar saƙon rubutu da aka aika wa waɗanda ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Gwamnati ba wai kawai ta yi amfani da wannan bayanin ba ne wajen gargadi 'yan kasa game da yiwuwar hulda da mutanen da ke dauke da cutar, amma kuma ta sanya bayanin wurin da suke a fili, saboda canje-canje masu yawa a dokokin kare bayanai da aka yi bayan barkewar cutar MERS a kasar.
Ana iya samun damar wannan bayanin ta hanyar aikace-aikace da shafukan yanar gizo. Kasashe, ciki har da Jamus, suna la'akari da amfani da tsarin da aka daidaita da kuma tsarin tsare sirri.
Har zuwa ranar 6 ga Afrilu, 2020 ba a bayyana cikakken bayani ba.
Binciken tuntuɓar sirri  yana da tsayayyen ra'ayi, tare da babban adadin wallafe-wallafen bincike wanda ya fara aƙalla 2013.
Duk da haka, PEPP-PT samfurin ne na kokarin daidaitawa wanda ya hada da tsarin tsakiya da kuma rarraba, kuma ba yarjejeniya ɗaya ba ce. Yarjejeniyar rarraba sun hada da rarraba bayanan sirri (DP-PPT/DP-3T), lambobin tuntuɓar lokaci (TCN, fka Contact EventNumbers, CEN), ladabi don tabbatar da tsare sirri, hanyoyin da za a bi don wayar salula (PACT) da sauransu.
Waɗannan hanyoyin suna tabbatar da cewa bayanan sirri ba su taɓa barin na'urar ba kuma duk abubuwan da aka yi daidai suna faruwa a kan na'urar.
The Privacy Group, MIT Media Lab suna ci gaba da samar da SafePaths, wani dandamali na tsare sirri da ke tattara da kuma amfani da bayanai game da wurin da kake ko kuma hanyar da kake bi don bin hanyar yaduwar COVID-19.
Aikin wannan dandamali ya dogara ne akan binciken da aka kawo a cikin takaddar Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic (Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic), wanda aka buga a watan Maris na 2020. Wani irin wannan aikin shine dandamali na SafeTrace, wanda Enigma MPC, kamfanin haɓaka fasahar tsare sirri, wanda kuma ya kafa MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace tana amfani da ingantacciyar fasahar kayan aiki da ke ba masu amfani damar raba bayanan sirri game da wurin zama da kuma lafiyarsu tare da sauran masu amfani da jami'ai ba tare da sanya sirrin waɗannan bayanan cikin haɗari ba.
A ranar 5 ga Afrilu, 2020, ƙungiyoyi masu irin wannan tsarin da kuma amfani da irin wannan yarjejeniya sun kafa TCN Global Coalition, wanda burinsa shine  rage rarrabuwa da kuma tabbatar da daidaiton aikace-aikacen sa ido da faɗakarwa na duniya, wanda shine mabuɗin don yaduwar su.
