An ba da shawarar nitasoxaniid don ƙarin bincike a cikin vivo, yana nuna hana SARS-CoV-2 a ƙananan maida hankali. Bincike ya nuna cewa don shigar SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar hulɗa tare da mai karɓar ACE2 yana buƙatar sulhunta furotin na spike tare da protease mai ɗaukar hoto na 2 (TMPRSS2).
Bincike kan amfani da chlorohine da hydroxychloroquine tare da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba yana da manyan ƙuntatawa waɗanda ke hana ƙungiyar likitanci amfani da waɗannan hanyoyin magani ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Ozeltamvir baya hana SARS-CoV-2 in vitro, kuma ba a san rawar da yake takawa wajen maganin COVID-19 ba.
Za a iya samun cutar hypercytokinemia a matsayin rikitarwa a lokacin da cutar ta COVID-19 ta yi tsanani.
Akwai tabbaci cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun halayen hypercytokinemia. A cikin wani karamin bincike da Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta Sin ta gudanar, an hada da tocilizumab a cikin shawarar da aka bayar kan maganin coronavirus.
Wannan magani ya shiga gwaji na biyu wanda ba a yi amfani da shi ba, wanda ake gudanarwa a matakin kasa a Italiya, bayan an samu sakamako mai kyau a kan marasa lafiya da ke da mummunar cutar.
An haɗa shi da gwajin jini don gano ciwon cytokine don magance abubuwan da ake tsammanin suna haifar da mutuwa a wasu marasa lafiya.
A cikin 2017, FDA ta amince da mai adawa da mai karɓar mai karɓar interleukin-6 bisa ga nazarin binciken baya-bayan nan don magance cutar cutar cytokine ta steroidal ta haifar da wani dalili, maganin T-cell CAR.
A yau, babu wata hujja da aka tsara ta bazuwar da aka sarrafa cewa tocilizumab yana da tasiri wajen magance cutar cytokine.
A halin yanzu ana ganin bayar da rigakafin da aka tsabtace da kuma mai da hankali da tsarin garkuwar jikin marasa lafiya da suka warke daga COVID-19 ya samar wa mutanen da suke bukatar su, a matsayin hanyar rigakafin da ba rigakafi ba.
An gwada wannan dabarar a kan marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar SARS, amma sakamakon ba shi da tabbaci.
Rashin cutar  wani sakamako ne da ake tsammani wanda maganin rigakafi na iya ba da kariya daga SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, ana iya amfani da wasu hanyoyin, kamar su ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙwayoyin cuta da ke dogara da antibody da / ko phagocytosis.
Sauran nau'ikan maganin rigakafi na wucewa, misali, ta amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta na monoclonal da aka ƙera, suna kan ci gaba.
Za a iya ƙara amfani da maganin jini mai sakewa, wanda ya ƙunshi ruwan jini daga marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma yana ɗauke da ƙwayoyin cuta da ke yaƙi da wannan cuta.
